$pearl_page_charity["about-us"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1499244730849{margin-top: -60px !important;padding-top: 60px !important;background-color: #fafafa !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2"][stm_video style="style_4" image="757" height="360" url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QIYcFth8ty4"][stm_spacer height="0" height_tablet="0" height_mobile="30"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Who we are" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]Charity — is a nonprofit organization that seeks to enable thousands of families and individuals in developing countries to achieve lasting self-reliance through online and classroom based job market education and one-on-one mentoring.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1499244790917{border-top-width: 1px !important;border-top-color: #bfbfbf !important;border-top-style: solid !important;}"] <blockquote>“Blessed are the peacemakers, for they shall be called sons of God.”</blockquote> <span class="blockquote-author">Richard Arkenstone</span>[/vc_column_text][stm_spacer height="55" height_tablet="30" height_mobile="0"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1497952248244{padding-top: 55px !important;background-color: #fafafa !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Our Story" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]<span style="color: #808080; font-size: 18px;"><strong>By 2007, Naomi Lawrence and Richard Arkenstone were convinced many key innovations in global development weren’t getting the attention they deserved.</strong></span> Believing there had to be a better way to do aid, they started an experiment. In March 2010, they invited any social entrepreneur to pitch his or her earth-changing idea at the World Conference Hall. The 100+ participants ranged from a group of ABC scientists to a woman who’d never before left her Kenyan village.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="765" img_size="640x360" alignment="right"][stm_spacer height="80" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="40"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" stm_parallax="enable" css=".vc_custom_1497942064658{background-image: url(http://pearl.stylemixthemes.com/charity/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2017/06/Fotolia_138226686.jpg?id=768) !important;}" stm_transparent_bg="rgba(89,30,0,0.6)"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-5 vc_col-md-5 vc_col-xs-12"][stm_spacer height="92" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][vc_column_text] <p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #fdb714;">MISSION</span></strong></p> <h3 style="text-align: center; font-weight: 400;"><span style="color: #ffffff;"><em>To catalyze a global market for ideas, information, and money that democratizes aid and philanthropy.</em></span></h3> [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-offset-2 vc_col-lg-5 vc_col-md-offset-2 vc_col-md-5 vc_col-sm-offset-0 vc_col-xs-12"][stm_spacer height="92" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][vc_column_text] <p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #fdb714;">VISION</span></strong></p> <h3 style="text-align: center; font-weight: 400;"><span style="color: #ffffff;"><em>Unleashed potential of people to make positive change happen.</em></span></h3> [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][stm_spacer height="225" height_tablet="210" height_mobile="210"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="5/6" offset="vc_col-lg-offset-2 vc_col-lg-8 vc_col-md-offset-2 vc_col-md-8 vc_col-sm-offset-1 vc_col-xs-12" css=".vc_custom_1502706890624{margin-top: -170px !important;padding-right: 55px !important;padding-left: 55px !important;}" el_class="sm_pd_0"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner css=".vc_custom_1499686499932{padding-top: 68px !important;padding-right: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 37px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;background-color: #fdb714 !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Our Core Values" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff" use_theme_fonts="yes" heading_line="no_line" heading_icon="stmicon-icon-title-shape" heading_icon_pos="bottom" heading_icon_color="custom" heading_icon_custom_color="#ffffff" css=".vc_custom_1497942729024{margin-bottom: 70px !important;}"][vc_column_text] <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px;"><span style="color: #ffffff;"><strong>Carityhas four core values that are more than just buzzwords. They’re at the center of our office culture and drive our daily work.</strong></span></p> [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1499144134522{padding-top: 80px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2"][stm_icon_box icon="stmicon-charity_head_time" icon_size="72" icon_width="70" style="style_7"] <h4>Always Open</h4> We believe in the power of great ideas and that these ideas can come from anyone, anywhere, at any time.[/stm_icon_box][stm_spacer height="75" height_tablet="75" height_mobile="40"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][stm_icon_box icon="stmicon-charity_binoculars" icon_width="70" style="style_7"] <h4>Listen, Act, Learn. Repeat.</h4> We continually experiment. We fail quickly and productively. We use data and feedback to guide our course.[/stm_icon_box][stm_spacer height="75" height_tablet="75" height_mobile="40"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][stm_icon_box icon="stmicon-charity_box" icon_size="74" icon_width="70" style="style_7"] <h4>Never Settle</h4> We have an obligation to question the rules, change them for the better, raise the bar, play a different game, and play it better than anyone thinks is possible.[/stm_icon_box][stm_spacer height="0" height_tablet="0" height_mobile="40"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][stm_icon_box icon="stmicon-charity_like" icon_size="63" icon_width="70" style="style_7"] <h4>Committed to WOW</h4> We act promptly, enthusiastically, and professionally so people are WOW-ed by their interactions with us.[/stm_icon_box][stm_spacer height="0" height_tablet="50" height_mobile="40"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1497953996557{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_column][stm_spacer height="110" height_tablet="80" height_mobile="60"][vc_custom_heading text="People Ready to Help" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes" heading_line="no_line" heading_icon="stmicon-icon-title-shape" heading_icon_pos="bottom" heading_icon_color="custom" heading_icon_custom_color="#808080" css=".vc_custom_1497953756558{margin-bottom: 75px !important;}"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3" offset="vc_col-lg-offset-2 vc_col-lg-8 vc_col-md-offset-2 vc_col-md-8 vc_col-sm-offset-2 vc_col-xs-12"][vc_column_text] <p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="font-size: 18px;">We’re curious, passionate, and committed to helping nonprofits learn and grow. Oh, and some of us are stage actors and worm farmers on the side.</strong></p> [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][stm_staff_container layout="grid" style="style_6" cols="4" carousel="true"][stm_staff name="Fred Ferguson" image="335" image_size="290x290" description="30 age, Sacramento" facebook="fb.com" twitter="twitter.com"][stm_staff name="Naomi Lawrence" image="329" image_size="290x290" description="56 age, Cupertino" facebook="#" twitter="#"][stm_staff name="Richard Arkenstone" image="330" description="58 age, Los Angeles" image_size="290x290" facebook="#"][stm_staff name="Amy Fowler" image="331" image_size="290x290" description="28 age, San Jose" facebook="#" twitter="#" insta="#"][stm_staff name="Brianne Hilton" image="1173" image_size="290x290" description="26 age, Sacramento" facebook="#" twitter="#" gplus="#" insta="#"][/stm_staff_container][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), '_edit_lock' => array ( 0 => '1502715267:1', ), '_edit_last' => a