$pearl_page_charity["single-donation"] = array ( 'content' => 'One of the most frustrating facts of modern life is that you need money in order to make money. If you have never thought about things in this way before, then you need to consider how the world works. What if you wanted to start a small business? Your first step would be to find investors. What if you wanted to build a home that would slowly increase your wealth as it increased in value? You need money to build that house. What if you want to go to college so that you can develop new skills that will put you at the top of your game? Again, you need money to go to college. The point that should be taken from these examples is that money making techniques are designed for people who already have money to begin with. You could give up here and decide that the world is simply unfair, or you could find ways to get money that will help you get on your feet. In order to be a winner, you need to start using federal grants. <ul> <li>Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in Latin literature from 45 BC.</li> <li>There are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available.</li> <li>Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text.</li> <li>Search for \'lorem ipsum\' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy.</li> <li>Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident.</li> <li>It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages</li> <li>The standard chunk of Lorem Ipsum used since the 1500s is reproduced below for those interested.</li> </ul> &nbsp;', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', 1 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', 2 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), '_edit_last' => array ( 0 => '1', 1 => '1', ), 'target_amount' => array ( 0 => '11000', 1 => '11000', ), ' donors_count' => array (